 where pets curl up after long walks, where kids scatter their toys, and where love quietly settles in.<br><br>Recently, we received a heartfelt message from Dr. Jill Caruso, a veterinarian in Brooklyn and the founder of Faithful Friends Animal Hospital. During a trip to the Turks and Caicos Islands, she was deeply moved by the number of stray dogs wandering the island without care or shelter. That experience led her to connect with <strong><a href="https://www.potcakeplace.com/" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Potcake Place K9 Rescue</span></a></strong>, a nonprofit organization working to bring those dogs to safety and find them loving homes. Dr. Caruso is now organizing a fundraiser to support their work, and she kindly invited Lany Space to take part. </p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-db2e" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dQEsWe gFKonE pf-437_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-deXguC bAaQfZ"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-438_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-439_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/dog_flyer.webp?v=1745206717" width="2550" height="3300" alt="dog flyer.webp__PID:424022d2-e425-4ca4-bb33-41b172ca56b8" title="Lany Space founder Vanessa and her daughter Olivia" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-dycZeM jfmvQi pf-440_ pf-image-1"/><h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-441_"><em>Potcake Place K9 Rescue fundraiser flyer.</em></h4></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-4ee0" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dQEsWe gFKonE pf-566_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-deXguC bAaQfZ"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-565_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-564_"><p 