ss="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-457_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Giving Back with Dog Friendly Rugs: Why It Matters</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-458_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-459_"><p class="sc-iapVNj evXKbL pf-460_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">When we first heard about the compassionate efforts at Potcake Place and <strong><a href="https://faithfulfriendsny.com/" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Faithful Friends Animal Hospital</span></a></strong>, our hearts were instantly touched. Our dog friendly rugs aren't simply décor; they're thoughtfully designed to handle the joyful chaos pets often bring into our lives. Easy to clean and durable, our rugs are ready to welcome wagging tails, playful paws, and the occasional unexpected mess.<br><br>But pet friendly rugs do more than withstand everyday life. They offer comfort and security to dogs recovering from trauma, surgeries, or the stress of shelter life. To us, a rug symbolizes safety, a gentle assurance to dogs who have never known comfort, warmth, or peace.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-570_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-569_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-568_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-567_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Lany Space Donates Rugs to Support Stray Dogs in Need</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-467_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-468_"><p class="sc-iapVNj evXKbL pf-469_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In collaboration with Faithful Friends Animal Hospital's fundraising event, we donated beautiful rugs valued at $4,794. These rugs were included in carefully assembled raffle baskets, helping to raise essential funds for Potcake Place K9 Rescue. Every dollar raised directly supports veterinary care, transportation, food, and vital supplies, paving the way for rescued dogs to find loving, permanent homes.<br><br>This initiative embodies our core belief: meaningful design should always carry purpose. Each rug gifted symbolizes our hope to bring warmth, healing, and happiness into the lives of animals who need it most.<br><br></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-626_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-625_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-624_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-623_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Meet Butch and Alphie: Two Rescue Dogs Looking for a Home</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-596_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:6;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-591_"><img title="Butch and Alphie" alt="Butch and Alphie" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/18c272a9e08f15efbcf192fbcf9eff2e.webp?v=1745209324&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/18c272a9e08f15efbcf192fbcf9eff2e.webp?v=1745209324&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/18c272a9e08f15efbcf192fbcf9eff2e.webp?v=1745209324&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/18c272a9e08f15efbcf192fbcf9eff2e.webp?v=1745209324&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shop