-h2"><i class="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-482_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Who Is Potcake Place K9 Rescue?</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-611_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-610_"><p class="sc-iapVNj evXKbL pf-609_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Potcake Place K9 Rescue is a nonprofit organization based in the beautiful Turks and Caicos Islands. Dedicated volunteers work tirelessly to reduce the number of homeless ''potcake''&nbsp;dogs, mixed-breed dogs native to the Caribbean islands. Due to limited veterinary resources on the islands, many of these gentle animals face severe health challenges.<br><br>Supported entirely by generous donations, Potcake Place provides essential medical care, nutritious food, loving foster homes, and ultimately, adoption opportunities in North America. Their unwavering commitment has brought thousands of island dogs to safety, forever changing their lives.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-519_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-520_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-521_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-522_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Why Pet Friendly Rugs Matter in Homes with Rescue Animals</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-540_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-541_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/a95d9bbb2f8789957ddeacb1cd9d0194.webp?v=1745212265" width="1332" height="888" 