-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-528_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-529_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-530_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Behind the Scenes: Raffle Baskets, Community Support and Photos from the Event</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-531_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-532_"><p class="sc-iapVNj evXKbL pf-533_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The fundraiser took place on October 19th, 2025, at Sirico's Caterers in Brooklyn, New York. Organized by Faithful Friends Animal Hospital, the event aimed to raise awareness and support for Potcake Place K9 Rescue, a nonprofit helping stray dogs from the Turks and Caicos Islands.<br><br>Lany Space proudly donated 18 rugs, valued at $4,794, to be included in raffle baskets prepared for the event. Each basket contributed to the fundraising efforts, with proceeds going toward medical care, transportation, and adoption services for rescued dogs. After the event, we received photos of Butch and Alphie: two six-month-old island dogs currently staying at Faithful Friends and looking for a permanent home. Seeing their hopeful eyes reminded us why this donation mattered.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-8fc3" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dQEsWe gFKonE pf-547_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-deXguC bAaQfZ"><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-548_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-549_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-550_ pf-heading-1-h2"><i class="sc-empmoP ftWFYg pf-551_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-star pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Join Us: Support Stray Dogs Through Style and Compassion</h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-552_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-553_"><p class="sc-iapVNj evXKbL pf-554_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">If you've ever shared your home with a pet, you know how quickly a space becomes something more. A favorite rug turns into a nap spot. A quiet corner becomes a place of comfort. At Lany Space, we are a small brand with a big heart. We believe that even the simplest choices can help create a kinder world. Every April, we celebrate our charity month by giving back through causes we care about. This year, that mission includes helping rescue dogs find warmth, safety, and a place to call home.<br><br>By supporting rescue efforts like Potcake Place, we hope to offer that same sense of comfort to dogs still waiting for a home. If you believe that softness can heal and small choices can make a difference, we invite you to <a href="http://lanyspace.com" target="_self"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">shop our full collection</span></strong></a> of rugs made for warm hearts, wagging tails, and homes that care.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>
